original_text: For each dam type, what is the average height and the maximum height?
rejected_translation: ¿Cuál es la altura promedio y la altura máxima para cada tipo de presa?
back_translation_text: What is the average and maximum height for each type of prey?

original_text: For each model, how many have a flat top rear sight, and how many have a case deflector? What is the average barrel length in inches?
rejected_translation: ¿Cuántos modelos tienen una visión plana hacia atrás y cuántos tienen un desvío de caja?
back_translation_text: How many models have a flat back view and how many have a box deflection?

original_text: Which districts had incumbents who were re-elected? List the district number, incumbent name, party, year first elected, and mention if there were any candidates who lost the renomination.
rejected_translation: Encuentra el número del distrito, el nombre del titular, el partido, el año en que fue elegido por primera vez, y menciona si hubo candidatos que perdieron la nominación.
back_translation_text: Find the district number, the name of the holder, the party, the year he was first elected, and mention if there were candidates who lost the nomination.

original_text: What is the percentage of second place finishes for each driver?
rejected_translation: ¿Cuál es el porcentaje de segundos puestos para cada piloto?
back_translation_text: What is the percentage of second places for each pilot?

original_text: Determine the airport with the highest total passengers and compute the average percentage change in passenger traffic from 2007/2008 for that airport.
rejected_translation: El objetivo de la Decisión de incoación de la Comisión es garantizar que los costes de transporte de pasajeros sean de conformidad con el artículo 107 del Tratado.
back_translation_text: The Commission's opening decision aims to ensure that passenger transport costs are in accordance with Article 107 of the Treaty.
